screen( "XBIOS Console" )
\#XBIOS\# Console Functions                                        <tos.h>
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Keyboard:
  \#Bioskeys\#  - reset translation tables
  \#Gettime\#   - read \link("%%GLOBAL%%")IKBD\# clock
  \#Ikbdws\#    - send control message to \link("%%GLOBAL%%")IKBD\#
  \#Initmouse\# - set mouse report parameters
  \#Kbdvbase\#  - get \link("%%GLOBAL%%")IKBD\# handler vectors
  \#Kbrate\#    - set key repeat rate
