Screen Dump:
  \#Prtblk\#    - partial dump
  \#Scrdmp\#    - full dump
  \#Setprt\#    - specify printer
\end

screen( "XBIOS I/O" )
\#XBIOS\# I/O Functions                                            <tos.h>
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Floppy:
  \#Flopfmt\#   - format track
  \#Floprate\#  - get/set floppy seek rate
  \#Floprd\#    - read sectors
  \#Flopver\#   - verify sectors
  \#Flopwr\#    - write sectors
  \#Protobt\#   - construct boot sector

Devices:
  \#Bconmap\#   - map device to BIOS device 1
  \#Iorec\#     - return device buffer
  \#Midiws\#    - write string to MIDI
  \#Rsconf\#    - set RS232 parameters

DMA:
  \#DMAread\#   - read ACSI/SCSI sectors
  \#DMAwrite\#  - write ACSI/SCSI sectors

Note: XBIOS I/O errors are not intercepted by the critical error
      handler.
\end

