  <color_index> is the desired color index.


Function changes the color for all line drawing functions.
It returns the color index implemented.

\#VDI Opcode\# 17

See also \#VDI Attributes\#, \#v_pline\#(), \#v_arc\#(), \#v_ellarc\#() and \#v_rbox\#().
\end

screen( capsensitive("vsl_ends") )
#include <vdi.h>

void vsl_ends( int handle, int beg_style, int end_style );

  <handle> is the \#VDI Handle\#.
  <beg_style> is used at the [0] end of the line:
  <end_style> is used at the other end of the line:
              SQUARE   =====  (default)
              ARROWED  <===>
              ROUND    *===*  (wide lines only)


Function changes ending style for all line drawing functions.

\#VDI Opcode\# 108

See also \#VDI Attributes\#, \#v_pline\#(), \#v_arc\#(), \#v_ellarc\#() and \#v_rbox\#().
