          1 - 24 for FIS_PATTERN (see \#vsf_interior\#).
          1 - 12 for FIS_HATCH (see \#vsf_interior\#).


Function changes the pattern used for interior filling. 
It returns the index selected.

Indexes 1-8 for FIS_PATTERN correspond to dither patterns of
increasing density (8 = solid).

