  <handle> is the \#VDI Handle\#.
  <string> is a NULL terminated text string.
           

Function prints <string> at the current cursor location in alpha mode.
It differs from \#v_curtext\#() in that it implements the following
special codes ('\\022' = DC2):

\\0220 - boldface on
\\0221 - boldface off
