Function sets the color attribute for \#draw_line\#(),
\#horizontal_line\#(), \#filled_rect\#() and \#filled_polygon\#().

See also \#Line A\#.
\end

screen( capsensitive("set_ln_mask") )
#include <linea.h>

void set_ln_mask( int mask );

  <mask> is the line pattern mask.


Function sets the line pattern for \#draw_line\#() and \#horizontal_line\#().

See also \#Line A\#.
