  <y1> is the y location of the top edge.
  <x2> is the x location of the right edge.
  <y2> is the y location of the bottom edge.
  <clip> option: 0 = turn off clipping.


Function sets the clipping rectangle for \#filled_rect\#() and
\#filled_polygon\#().

See also \#Line A\#.
\end

