  <scale> 0 = no scaling.
  <style> bitmap for effects:
          1 = bold, 2 = light, 4 = underline, 8 = outline
  <chup> rotation in 0.1 degrees: 0, 900, 1800 or 2700.
  <text_fg> text foreground color (see \#Bit Planes\#).
  <text_bg> text background color (see \#Bit Planes\#).


Function sets the attributes for \#text_blt\#().

See also \#Line A\#.
\end

