  <signal> contains 0 to clear all pending signals, or a new signal.
  <f> is an open \#I/O handle\# for a process pseudo-file.


Function is used to continue a process in trace mode.

See also \#MiNT Process\# and \#Signals\#.
\end

screen( "PTRACEFLOW" )
GO - Flow Trace Mode                                \#Fcntl Command Code\#
----------------------------------------------------------------------
\#Fcntl\#( PTRACEFLOW, signal, f );

  <signal> contains 0 to clear all pending signals, or a new signal.
